node.text: @hypefoods: For the first installment of the new 'Blended' series — a food-focused offshoot of How To showcasing delicious fusions— HYPEBEAST recently visited @pokeburriphilly, where restaurant manager Jessy showed us how an “everything” sushi donut is made.

#hypeAF: @mezcotoyz has released a three-foot figure of the King of the Monsters: Godzilla. The massive collectible figure measures at 18-inches in height and comes with 10 points of articulation, a hinged jaw, and a tail with an internal skeleton armature. Pre-order yours now for $450 USD on the Mezco Toyz website.⁠⁠
Photo: Mezco Toyz

node.text:
@hypebeastsports: @mannypacquiao has officially announced his run for president in the 2022 Philippine elections. The 42 year old boxer recently accepted the nomination from his PDP-Laban Party and also took to Twitter to urge support from his community and endorsement as the country’s next candidate for change. Head to the link in bio for more details.⁠
Photo: Chris Hyde/Getty Images

@hypegolf: Here's another look at @champagnepapi's @officialnocta x @nikegolf Collection. Mark your calendars for its release via @nike SNKRS on September 23.⁠⁠
Photo: Nike

node.text:
@hypebeastcarclub:⁠ All 300 U.S. designated units of @acura's 2022 NSX Type S were reserved in under 24 hours — with another 100 on a waitlist. Starting at around $170,000 USD, the latest version was expected to be in high demand granted its celebrated history as one of @honda‘s icons. Hit the link in the bio for more details.⁠
Photo: Honda

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: @nike is preparing a batch of “Toasty” Dunk makeups that are built to withstand the colder months. The latest iteration to be unveiled is a Dunk Low Toasty “Sequoia” colorway, whose nominal shade graces the fleece interiors and a majority of the insulated uppers. Orange accents are dispersed to the Swooshes and heel overlays, while down below, white midsoles atop gum traction round out the look. Hit the link in bio for details.⁠⁠
Photo: Nike

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on September 19, 2021 tagging @sothebys, and @hypeart. May be an image of text that says 'HYPEBEAST HYPEB Û form Û AN ULTRA-RARE COPY OF THE US CONSTITUTION WILL GO ON AUCTION THIS NOVEMBER Estimated to fetch $15 million to $20 million USD.'.

node.text:
@hypeart: @sothebys is auctioning one of the original 11 copies of the US constitution this November. The record is “one of the most rare and coveted historical documents that has ever come to auction" and is expected to fetch around $15 million to $20 million USD. Learn more via the link in bio.⁠
Photo: Ed Jones/Getty Images
